5154 - Livestock Summary > COMMONWEALTH HILL PROPRIETARY LIMITED is an Australian proprietary company. Its operations cover livestock. The company is not involved in the import or export of goods. COMMONWEALTH HILL PROPRIETARY LIMITED is headquartered in Port Augusta, South Australia. It is headed by CEO Hugh Glasgow Maclachlan. For the 2024 financial year, the company reported revenue of $32.38 million. Its net profit totalled $10.46 million. COMMONWEALTH HILL PROPRIETARY LIMITED forms part of the wholesale trade industry sector.
